Dialogue: 1,0:00:20.47,0:00:24.98,Blue title,,0,0,0,,{TIME:20479,24983}{\blur0.75\fs100\pos(1170,900)}The Cursed One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.47,0:00:24.98,Black Title,,0,0,0,,{TIME:20479,24983}{\blur0.75\fs150\pos(906,346)}Kaori
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.57,0:00:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:28570,30614}{\i1}It's lovely…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.40,0:00:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:31406,34576}This… is for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.24,0:00:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:38247,39873}Kaori, are you ready yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.99,0:00:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:40999,42292}Sorry, I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.21,0:00:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:43210,45045}Kaori will be thrilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.04,0:00:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:45045,46922}I'm sure it will look good on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:46922,50259}{\i1}Takayuki-niisan is\Nmy mom's younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.92,0:00:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:50926,54304}{\i1}It came as a shock\Nwhen he got married last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.30,0:00:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:54304,56640}{\i1}It's made him much more gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.64,0:01:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:56640,60477}{\i1}I just know that Takayuki-niisan\Nhas to be my prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.47,0:01:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:60477,62145}That sounds serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.52,0:01:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:63522,64064}I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.36,0:01:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:76368,77369}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.49,0:01:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:81498,85669}Women sure are scary, huh?\NI didn't know they could change this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.66,0:01:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:85669,87921}You're exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.92,0:01:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:87921,91049}No, I mean it. You look really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.04,0:01:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:91049,92175}It really suits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.26,0:01:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:93260,94761}{\i1}Takayuki-niisan…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.93,0:01:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:103937,107941}{\i1}If I wore that,\NI could dance with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:131506,133216}Oh, no…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.59,0:02:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:133592,135469}I must have fallen asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:135469,136678}There must have been a power cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:140098,142059}Oh, no. What have I…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.68,0:02:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142684,147022}I must have put this on last night\Nwhen thinking of Takayuki-niisan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.73,0:02:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147731,148982}That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150525,153153}What a relief that it didn't get creased.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:168960,169878}{\i1}Was that me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:02:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176885,178804}{\i1}Or was it Mom's?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.93,0:03:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179930,183058}Oh, wait.\NIt's just Dad coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187187,192526}Darling, it's late, why are you\Ngoing to that woman's place again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192526,194820}Don't you care about Kaori?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.15,0:03:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196154,197364}Darling…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:199324,200659}Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201284,202119}Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.91,0:03:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202911,203787}Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205455,206373}Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207165,209459}Kaori, it's time to get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212754,214548}What are you doing, Kaori?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.51,0:03:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:219511,224558}I know you're happy,\Nbut it's childish to go to sleep in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:225684,227436}I was…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.43,0:03:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:227436,229062}{\i1}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229062,231732}I changed! I really did!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231732,235944}What are you talking about?\NHurry up and wash your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236695,238905}Mom, where's Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239865,242701}He's working, like he usually is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245787,249541}{\i1}I feel so sorry for her…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:252043,256256}Maybe my mom's neurosis\Nrubbed off on me…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256256,257299}Neurosis?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257299,259050}Has something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259050,261762}It's just…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261762,264639}I'm not sure what\Nhappened last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264639,269019}When I woke up, I was wearing\Nthe one piece. I'm sure I took it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.01,0:04:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269019,270729}One piece?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270729,273899}You sure you weren't just tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273899,275650}I wonder about that…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:276568,277402}All rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283408,285160}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.16,0:04:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285160,288079}Oh… it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288079,289831}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289831,293668}{\i1}How… did it get like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299716,302344}It's all because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:306806,308433}{\i1}But it's so pretty…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313188,316775}{\i1}Takayuki-niisan, please save me…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326910,328078}Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329162,330455}Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331164,332582}Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333291,334459}Kaori!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.29,0:05:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336294,340340}You have to stop this, it's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.59,0:05:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:341591,343051}What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:05:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356231,357607}Kaori?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:06:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357607,360777}Kaori!\NKaori, get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:376668,377377}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379671,384426}I'm thankful that you\Ncame all this way, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388972,391892}It's better if you just look from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391892,394519}If she notices you, she'll get excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:405071,408742}No matter how many times\Nshe changes, it's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409701,411202}It's that one piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413038,414164}It keeps coming back?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.99,0:06:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414998,419669}At first, I tried\Nto take the one piece off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419669,426801}Then my brother and I tried to do tear it,\Nbut it wouldn't come off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426801,428970}It wouldn't work, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.97,0:07:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428970,433558}But the other day, after touching it,\NI finally understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433558,437562}It's just her skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439439,442233}That's just what it has become.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.23,0:07:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442233,446696}It hurts her if you pinch it.\NAnd when you look close…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446696,450742}You can even see its veins.\NStrange, isn't it?
